text: Mustafić is a patronymic Bosnian surname. People with the name include: * Fahrudin Mustafić (born 1981), Singapore footballer of Bosnian descent * Ibran Mustafić (born 1960), Bosnian politician * Muhamed Mustafić (born 1981), Bosnian handballer ==References== Category:Bosnian-language surnames Category:Patronymic surnames
title: Mustafić
